Package Main.MVCTest

Class GameBoardTest

java.lang.Object
Main.MVCTest.GameBoardTest
class GameBoardTest
extends java.lang.Object
GameBoardTest tests to see if the methods of GameBoard class which are all setters and getters are all working properly. The getters are tested first to ensure that they are working before using them to test the setters.
